label.value: 09320 - processed or preserved vegetables and similar (efsa foodex2)

definition.value: The category includes processed or preserved vegetables, including mushrooms, algae, mosses and lichens. The main processes included are canning, salting, preserving with sugar, drying, fermenting and pickling.
